Value: Altium Limited develops and sells computer software for the design of electronic products in the United States and internationally. It operates through Board and Systems; Microcontrollers and Embedded Systems; and Nexar segments. The company offers printed circuit board (PCB) design software products, including Altium Designer, Altium NEXUS, CircuitStudio, and CircuitMaker. It also provides Altium 365 cloud platform; Altium Concord Pro, a solution for library management; and Octopart, search engine for electronic parts. The company serves automotive, aerospace/defense, life sciences, mobile devices and communication, consumer electronics, electronics and hi-tech, research and education, industrial controls automation, computers, and semiconductors industries. Altium Limited was founded in 1985 and is headquartered in La Jolla, California.
